Resolve workspace & dataset GUIDs using the Power BI REST API

pbi_resolve_ids_from_connstr.Rd

Resolve workspace & dataset GUIDs using the Power BI REST API

Usage

pbi_resolve_ids_from_connstr(
  connstr,
  access_token,
  api_base = "https://api.powerbi.com/v1.0/myorg"
)

Arguments

connstr

Connection string used to infer workspace & dataset names.

access_token

OAuth2 bearer token for the Power BI API.

api_base

API base URL. Defaults to "https://api.powerbi.com/v1.0/myorg".

Value

A list with group_id, dataset_id, workspace, and dataset.
